'''Rogue Wave '''are an American indie rock band.

Their song "No Time" is featured on ''[[Iron Man 3: Heroes Fall – Music Inspired by the Motion Picture]]'', an album with music inspired by (but not used in) ''[[Iron Man 3]]''.

